  "prompt": "Where are the products of Coca-Cola manufactured?",
  "response": "Coca-Cola products are manufactured in numerous facilities located around the world. The Coca-Cola Company operates and works with bottling partners to produce its beverages through a franchise system. Some key locations include:\n\n1. North America: The United States (many plants across numerous states), Canada, and Mexico.\n2. Latin America: Countries such as Brazil, Argentina, Chile, and Colombia.\n3. Europe: The UK, Germany, France, Italy, and Spain, among others.\n4. Asia-Pacific: China, Japan, India, Australia, and South Korea.\n5. Africa: South Africa, Nigeria, Egypt, etc.\n6. Middle East: Countries including Saudi Arabia and the UAE.\n\nThese manufacturing facilities handle different aspects of production, including bottling, packaging, and distribution to meet the demand for Coca-Cola's wide range of products.",
